{"tha-ap456:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap456:0.2":"Jagatidayakavagga ","tha-ap456:0.3":"4 Tinukkadhariyattheraapadana ","tha-ap456:1.1":"“Padumuttarabuddhassa, ","tha-ap456:1.2":"bodhiya padaputtame; ","tha-ap456:1.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap456:1.4":"tayo ukke adharayim. ","tha-ap456:2.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap456:2.2":"soham ukkamadharayim; ","tha-ap456:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap456:2.4":"ukkadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap456:3.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap456:3.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap456:3.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap456:4.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap456:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap456:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap456:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap456:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap456:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap456:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma tinukkadhariyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap456:7.1":"Tinukkadhariyattherassapadanam catuttham. "}